[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0285","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0338","title":"CVS 1.10.7 可预测临时文件名本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVS 1.10.7 版本在文件锁定机制中使用可预测的临时文件名，本地攻击者可通过在合法 CVS 用户创建锁目录之前预先创建同名锁目录，导致 CVS 服务无法正常获取文件锁，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可利用，影响 CVS 1.10.7 及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.5，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0338"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.520","remediation":"升级 CVS 至 1.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复可预测临时文件名问题。如无法升级，可通过 umask 限制本地用户对锁目录的访问权限；建议迁移至 Subversion (SVN) 或 Git 替代 CVS。作为临时缓解，可配置严格的本地文件系统权限防止非授权用户创建锁目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1136","http://www.securityfocus.com/frames/?content=/templates/archive.pike%3Flist%3D1%26msg%3D20000423174038.A520%40clico.pl","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19870","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0338.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0338","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0338.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0338.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fxq-3r3p-42m4/GHSA-5fxq-3r3p-42m4.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_0_100.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-412.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0285.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0285.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0285.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0321","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0321.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0320","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9169,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10856}}","description":"Qualcomm Qpopper 2.53 及 3.0 版本在处理邮件消息时存在缺陷，未能正确识别标识消息文本结尾的换行符（\\n），导致缓冲区处理异常。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送长度为 1023 个字符且以 \\n 结尾的特制消息行触发该漏洞，从而造成拒绝服务或损坏邮箱数据。该漏洞影响使用 Qpopper 2.53/3.0 的邮件服务器，攻击者仅需向目标邮箱投递恶意邮件即可利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0320"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.230","remediation":"建议将 Qualcomm Qpopper 升级至 3.0.1 或更高版本（官方已修复 fgets 对 1023 字符行尾 \\n 的解析缺陷）。若无法立即升级，可在邮件网关或防火墙侧限制单封邮件每行长度不超过 1022 字节，并部署反垃圾邮件网关过滤超长畸形邮件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1133","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=9763.000421%40SECURITY.NNOV.RU","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0320.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0320","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0320.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0320.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/qpopper_euidl.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5vvr-mcc4-v73q/GHSA-5vvr-mcc4-v73q.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0320.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001309.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0321.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0317","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0317.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0318","title":"Atrium Mercur Mail Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Atrium Mercur Mail Server 3.2 存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可利用路径遍历技术（../）绕过目录限制，访问其他用户的电子邮件文件，或在邮件服务器系统中创建任意恶意文件。该漏洞影响所有版本 Atrium Mercur Mail Server 3.2，允许恶意本地用户窃取电子邮件隐私并植入恶意代码。漏洞原理源于对用户输入的文件路径验证不足，导致未授权的文件系统访问。CVSS 评分为 7.5（高级别严重程度），需本地访问权限即可利用，但潜在风险包括敏感数据泄露和系统完全失控。攻击者仅需具备基本的路径遍历技术即可轻易执行攻击，通过利用标准访问权限即可威胁邮件服务器的安全完整性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0318"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:27.977","remediation":"升级至 Mercur Mail Server 3.3 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历缺陷。由于此产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Active Directory 支持的邮件服务器。作为临时缓解措施，在 NTFS 层面限制普通用户对邮件存储目录的读取权限，并禁用 Web 邮件接口的路径回溯功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/2000-q2/0057.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1144","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0318.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0318","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0318.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0318.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f4mw-6gjr-pj7w/GHSA-f4mw-6gjr-pj7w.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mercure_imap_read_any_file.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0318.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001308.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e18a803826f5de26e56a6a31273d1b83fad61ed6/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0317.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0280","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0280.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0336","title":"OpenLDAP 符号链接本地任意文件修改漏洞","description":"Linux OpenLDAP 服务器在处理临时文件时存在符号链接（symlink）安全漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 `/usr/tmp/` 目录下创建恶意符号链接，诱使 OpenLDAP 服务器以提升的权限写入目标文件，从而实现任意文件修改。该漏洞影响 OpenLDAP 1.2.7/1.2.8/1.2.9/1.2.10 版本，利用需要本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0336"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:30.277","remediation":"升级到 OpenLDAP 1.2.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复符号链接跟踪问题。临时缓解措施：确保 /usr/tmp/ 目录设置 sticky bit（chmod +t /usr/tmp），并避免在多用户环境下以 root 权限运行 slapd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2000-012.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1232","http://www.turbolinux.com/pipermail/tl-security-announce/2000-May/000009.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19946","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0336.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0336","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0336.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0336.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-7rcw-76jx-qx7m/GHSA-7rcw-76jx-qx7m.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mandrake_MDKSA-2000-003.nasl","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--71b80b21-88e5-4eb6-903e-a2fe8f548491.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0336.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0280.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0258","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0295","title":"LCDproc 0.4 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"LCDProc 0.4 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 screen_add 命令发送特制数据触发该漏洞，导致目标系统以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 LCDProc 0.4 及更早版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前官方已发布修复版本，建议用户立即升级。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0295"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:25.167","remediation":"升级 LCDproc 至 0.5.7 或更高版本，该版本已修复 screen_add 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，配置 LCDd 绑定监听地址为 127.0.0.1（在 LCDd.conf 中设置 Listen=127.0.0.1），并在防火墙层面限制外部对 TCP 13666 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/7829","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/305589/30/26390/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1131","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.3.96.1000421010946.15318I-200000%40schizo.strange.net","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4315","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19868"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0332","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0332.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0331","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 命令处理器缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统中的命令处理器（CMD.EXE）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长环境变量触发该漏洞，导致命令处理器缓冲区溢出，造成目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞被命名为\"格式错误的环境变量\"漏洞，影响 Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统，需本地用户权限触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0331"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:29.623","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 发布的安全更新 (MS00-027)，限制本地用户通过超长环境变量触发 CMD.EXE 缓冲区溢出。如无法安装补丁，应限制非授权用户的本地登录权限，并监控异常进程创建行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0147.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1135","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-027","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0331.json","https://github.com/biggerwing/nsfocus-rsas-knowledge-base/blob/156208b301d4649ead13cd15f827830d08245b89/example","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qjvx-wh8v-928g/GHSA-qjvx-wh8v-928g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--72481ae7-0229-4d43-ae7d-7e12d475e6a5.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0332.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0243","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0243.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0268","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10624,\"inputTokens\":195,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10837}}","description":"Cisco IOS 11.x 和 12.x 版本的 Telnet 守护进程存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可在 Telnet 服务尚未就绪接收连接前发送 ENVIRON 选项，触发守护进程异常导致设备重启。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 11.x 至 12.0.7 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过发送特制 Telnet 协议包即可使目标设备重启，造成服务中断。CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中等危害级别的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0268"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.700","remediation":"建议将受影响的 Cisco IOS 设备升级至已修复该漏洞的版本（12.0(7.3)、12.0.7.XE1、11.3(9) 及后续版本，或 12.1 主线）。如无法立即升级，可在 VTY 线路配置中通过 access-class 限制可发起 Telnet 连接的源 IP，或在边界过滤 TCP 23 端口的 Telnet 流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/707/iostelnetopt-pub.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/1289","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1123","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0268.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0268.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0268","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0268.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0268.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c43m-vj32-q46r/GHSA-c43m-vj32-q46r.json","https://github.com/arpitn30/nipper-ng/blob/a344e58392d528c168b74ccda5caa309923fff56/0.11.10/common/report-vulns.c","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1123/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0243.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0241","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0241.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0267","title":"Cisco Catalyst CatOS 5.4.x 使能密码认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 交换机运行 CatOS 5.4 版本时存在使能（enable）密码认证绕过漏洞，攻击者只要能够与设备进行 CLI 交互（通过控制台、Telnet 或 SSH 登录到用户模式），无需输入正确的使能密码便可直接执行 enable 命令进入特权模式，从而完全控制交换机。该漏洞影响 Catalyst 系列运行 5.4.x 版本的设备，可导致攻击者篡改配置、劫持流量或造成拒绝服务，属中危漏洞，CVSS 评分约 4.6。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0267"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.513","remediation":"升级到 Cisco CatOS 5.4(1) 或更高版本以修复使能密码旁路漏洞。如无法立即升级，应通过 enable password 命令配置强加密使能口令，并限制管理访问来源，仅允许受信任管理员通过控制台或带外管理接口登录设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/707/catos-enable-bypass-pub.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/1288","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1122"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0241.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0302","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0302.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0311","title":"Microsoft Windows 2000 Active Directory 未受保护属性信息篡改漏洞","description":"Windows 2000 域控制器存在 Mixed Object Access 漏洞。Active Directory 支持基于属性的访问控制，但在特定组合操作场景下，已认证的攻击者可修改其本无权限修改的对象属性。攻击者需拥有域内有效凭据并具备网络访问权限。该漏洞仅影响作为域控制器使用的 Windows 2000 Server 和 Advanced Server，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。成功利用可导致目录信息被篡改。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0311"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-20","updated":"2000-04-20","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-026 提供的安全更新补丁，下载地址为 https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?FamilyId=7237F230-A28B-447B-9034-6654DD7CD05E。同时在域控制器上配置 Active Directory 对象 ACL 权限，限制非管理员用户的写入权限。对于仍在使用 Windows 2000 的环境，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本以获取持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1145","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-026"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0302.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0240","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0272","title":"RealNetworks RealServer 端口 7070 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"RealNetworks RealServer 在处理 RTSP 协议流量时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向服务器 7070 端口发送畸形数据包，导致 RealServer 进程崩溃停止响应，需要手动重启服务才能恢复正常功能。该漏洞影响多个平台的 RealServer 版本，攻击门槛极低且效果显著。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0272"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-20","updated":"2000-04-20","remediation":"升级到 RealServer 7.0.1 或更高版本，或联系 RealNetworks 获取官方安全补丁并安装，同时建议在网络边界限制对 7070 端口的未授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-01T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0272","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95625288231045&w=2","http://service.real.com/help/faq/servg270.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1128","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19856"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19856"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0800","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0256","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9171,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10860}}","description":"FrontPage 97 与 98 的服务器扩展组件中，htimage.exe 与 Imagemap.exe 在处理服务器端图像映射（Image Map）请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于程序未对用户输入的映射参数进行长度校验，远程攻击者可通过构造超长的恶意请求数据发送至此组件，触发缓冲区溢出。成功利用后，攻击者可绕过网站原有的访问控制限制，执行本不应被允许的操作（如越权访问或执行代码）。该漏洞影响部署了 FrontPage 97/98 Server Extensions 的 Web 服务器，攻击者仅需能访问站点图像映射功能、无需身份认证即可发起攻击，CVSS 评分为 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0256"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.110","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器中删除或重命名 htimage.exe 与 Imagemap.exe（通常位于 /_vti_bin/ 及 /_vti_bin/_vti_adm/ 目录），禁用服务端图像映射功能；在 IIS 中移除非必要的 FrontPage Server Extensions，或升级至已修复的 Microsoft FrontPage 2000 Server Extensions / 更新版 FrontPage（如 SR-1.2 及以上）。临时缓解可在防火墙或 IIS 中拒绝向 *_vti_bin/* 路径的 htimage/Imagemap 请求，并仅允许受信任 IP 访问管理目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/470458/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1117","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-028","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/34720","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19853","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0256.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0256","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0256.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0256.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/fp_htimage.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-52gp-xhpr-89c9/GHSA-52gp-xhpr-89c9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a7e0266e-b8bd-4b3c-a22e-e545ec3c0403.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1117/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0800.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0800.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0282","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0282.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0292","title":"Adtran MX2800 M13 复用器以太网接口拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Adtran MX2800 M13 多路复用器以太网接口存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标设备的以太网接口发送大量 ICMP Ping 数据包实施洪水攻击，导致设备处理器过载并崩溃重启，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响运行特定固件版本的 Adtran MX2800 M13 多路复用器设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0292"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:24.773","remediation":"联系 Adtran 获取 MX2800 最新固件更新并安装，以修复以太网接口处理 ICMP 数据包时的缺陷。如无法升级，可在网络边界配置访问控制列表（ACL），限制对 MX2800 以太网接口的 ICMP 流量速率，或仅允许受信任管理 IP 地址访问该接口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1129","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.10004190908140.32750-100000%40localhost.localdomain"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0282.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0231","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0231.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0257","title":"Novell NetWare 5.1 Remote Administration Utility 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5.1 的远程 Web 管理工具（Remote Administration Utility）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，其原因是该工具在处理 HTTP 请求时未对 URL 长度进行有效校验。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标系统的管理端口发送一个超长的 URL 请求，即可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃引发拒绝服务，或进一步覆盖返回地址执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare 5.1 版本，攻击条件较低，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0257"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","remediation":"升级到 Novell NetWare 5.1 的官方补丁版本（Service Pack 或 NetWare 5.1 Support Pack 2 及以上），并限制远程管理端口（默认 TCP 8008/8009）仅允许受信任的内部 IP 访问，或在防火墙上禁用该端口的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1118","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.21.0004171825340.10088-100000%40nimue.tpi.pl","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19854","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0257.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0231.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0231.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0250","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0271","title":"GNU Emacs 本地密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"GNU Emacs 20 版本中存在本地窃听漏洞。其 read-passwd 等 Lisp 函数未能正确清除最近输入按键的历史记录，导致本地攻击者可通过访问按键历史记录读取用户输入的未加密密码。该漏洞影响 GNU Emacs 20 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，可通过查看按键历史记录窃取用户输入的明文密码。CVSS 评分 4.6，属于中等危害等级。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0271"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.133","remediation":"建议升级至 GNU Emacs 21.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 read-passwd 等 Lisp 函数不清除按键历史的缺陷。若无法立即升级，可禁用密码回显历史记录功能或限制本地用户访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1125","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-04-15&msg=tg4s8zioxq.fsf%40mercury.rus.uni-stuttgart.de","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/067b58f5ad5d89a104fab4ddd25fa3685c59a18e/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0271.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0271","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0271.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0271.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7mr4-hhph-pp56/GHSA-7mr4-hhph-pp56.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0271.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fe2ed06b-8f42-45aa-8a37-c96c4301eb76.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ce9ef916bfcfa71e15bd79861b0ea3312f7ed373/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0250.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0248","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0270","title":"GNU Emacs 临时文件可预测符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"GNU Emacs 20 的 make-temp-name Lisp 函数在创建临时文件时使用可预测的文件名，导致攻击者能够提前创建符号链接指向这些临时文件。当 Emacs 进程向这些可预测名称的临时文件写入敏感数据时，实际上会写入攻击者控制的符号链接目标，从而实现本地信息窃听。该漏洞影响 Emacs 20 版本，攻击者需具备在目标系统上创建符号链接的本地权限，成功利用后可导致敏感会话数据、密码或其他机密信息被非法获取。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0270"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.010","remediation":"建议升级至 GNU Emacs 20.7 或更高版本（如 Emacs 21.1+），修复 make-temp-name 可预测临时文件名漏洞。若暂时无法升级，请设置 TMPDIR 环境变量指向权限 700 的私有目录（如 ~/.tmp），并设置 umask 077 限制临时文件权限，防止符号链接攻击。同时避免在多用户可写目录（如 /tmp）中使用 make-temp-name 创建敏感临时文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1126","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-04-15&msg=tg4s8zioxq.fsf%40mercury.r